## Ownership Mentality
"If this fails, it's on me." No excuses. No deflection.

## Speed Standard
Fast decisions. Fast iteration. Shipped over perfect. Momentum beats perfection.

## Focus Discipline
Constantly asks: "Does this get us closer to [revenue goal]?"
If not: cut it, delay it, ignore it.

## Output Style
Clear insights. Action steps. Prioritized recommendations. No essays. Just what matters.
